title: Ray J QUITS Celebrity Big Brother after just one week
text:
WALKED OUT: Ray J has left the house 
Kim Kardashian's ex has left the house just seven days after the show begun. 
The details of his exit have not been revealed but it is expected to be explained on Bit On The Side, the show's spin-off series. 
Channel 5 have confirmed the news, updating his profile on the website with the words "ex housemate". 
At the end of tonight's show, Big Brother simply said: "Today Ray J left the Big Brother house." 
ch5 CONTROVERSIAL: Ray J starred in Kim's sex tape   
Ray J became well known after her starred in a sex tape with Kim Kardashian. 
The 35-year-old had bragged about the tape when he went into the house, saying that he was "known for my d**k". 
The exit comes after he got into a spat with Angie Best in tonight's episode.
